---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Privacy Policy | RealtyCopilot" description="Privacy policy for RealtyCopilot.app real estate calculator tools.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-14">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none text-gray-600 space-y-4">
      <p>Last updated: January 2025</p>
      <p>RealtyCopilot.app is a free, static calculator tool. We do not collect, store, or sell any personal data. All calculations are performed entirely in your browser — no data is sent to our servers.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800">Data We Don't Collect</h2>
      <p>We do not require account registration, collect financial information you enter into calculators, use cookies for tracking, or sell data to third parties.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800">Analytics</h2>
      <p>We may use privacy-respecting, cookie-free analytics (e.g., page view counts) to understand usage. No personally identifiable information is collected.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800">Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions? Contact us at privacy@realtycopilot.app.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
